review_title: Some good, but just not fun
one_reviews_text: Parts of this game had really high production values, but overall it just wasn't fun, especially the weapons/combat.  Can't recommend.

review_title: Different & Fun take on FPS Wave shooter
one_reviews_text: I have been enjoying this game quite a bit. The Setting (1890's London) is very cool, the weapons are very different and cool. There is alot of content here and I think well worth the $14.99 price tag. a definate buy!!

This is real Victorian London adventure. You can use total free movement and see scenes in details. Rich story more, arcade dynamic missions + many different type of enemies to fight with with. I recommend to use voice commands - they works great and make gameplay more cool!
